ly occurs in medieval records, while the vernacular form <i>Maud</i> was the one in everyday use. <i>Matilda</i> was revived in England as a learned form in the 18th century."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mathilde d'HAFFRINGUES was born in 1205, in Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France. She had at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1205–":"1205–Surnud","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1205–Female":"1205–Surnud","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","Affringues, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1205–":"1205–Kuollut","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1205–Female":"1205–Kuollut","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","Affringues, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Ranska"},"fr":{"1205–":"1205–Décédée","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","1205–Female":"1205–Décédée","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","Affringues, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France","lifeSummary":"Mathilde d'HAFFRINGUES est née en 1205, à Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1205–":"1205–Verstorben","1225–Female":"1225–Verstorben","1205–Female":"1205–Verstorben","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","Affringues, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Mathilde d'HAFFRINGUES wurde 1205 in Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Frankreich geboren. Sie hatte mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1205–":"1205–Desede","1225–Female":"1225–Desede","1205–Female":"1205–Desede","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","Affringues, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Affringues, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France"},"hu":{"1205–":"1205–elhunyt","1225–Female":"1225–elhunyt","1205–Female":"1205–elhunyt","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","Affringues, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Ca